@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nPOST /api/wallets/by-email/:email/topup" as API
participant "Database\nTable: Wallet" as WalletDB
participant "Database\nTable: Transaction" as TxDB
participant "Ethereum/Hardhat" as Chain
User->UI: Enter the token top-up amount
UI->API: Submit top-up request
API->WalletDB: Update wallet balance
WalletDB-->API: Wallet balance updated
API->TxDB: Store top-up transaction
TxDB-->API: Transaction stored successfully
API->Chain: Publish verification proof
Chain-->API: Return txHash and block metadata
API->TxDB: Update verification status
TxDB-->API: Verification updated
API-->UI: Return top-up result
UI-->User: Display updated wallet balance and transaction details

@enduml
